BoilerPlate - Common Code

BoilerPlate Generator - Common Code Generator
    Its a global script that generates basic project


Create-React-App this generates basic react application
react-native this generates basic react native application
create-react-native-app this generates react native application which is integrated with Expo

Angular-cli  this generates basic angular Code/project
ionic-cli this generates baisc ionic project


Create-React-App => generates basic React Project which has modules
    React
    ReactDOM
    Babel
    Webpack
    ...

npm => node package manager
    npm install moduleName - installing modules at project level
    npm install -g moduleName => installing modules globally
    npm install moduleName --save => install + add module to package.json
    npm install moduleName --save-dev => install + add module to devDependency section of package.json
    npm install moduleName@version => install module of that version

npm install -g create-react-app
npm install react-native-cli
npm install -g create-react-native-app
npm install -g angular-cli

Node    
    ES5
        export
        require
    ES6
        export - import with same name
        export default - can be imported by any reference name
        import


