Creating the project
    create-react-app demo
        Interally Creates Node Project
        Adds Modules like React ReactDOM React-Scripts
        Creates html page with empty root
        Creates js files for injecting components into root element

Create-React-App - default React Project
mern.io - Project with MongoDB, Express, React, Node
mean.io - Project with MongoDB, Express, Angular, Node
hospital mern - Project with default hospital modules
school mern - Project with default school modules

Project - demo - Project Structure
    node_modules - default folder for node modules
    public - default html 
    src - javascript files - index.js

Routing - Navigation between pages
    module - react-router-dom

npm install react-router-dom --save




































